{"tid":2087120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七旬清潔工人涉手捉警棍　被控阻差辦公　獲保釋候訊","createTime":"2020-06-30T14:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T15:00:27.000Z","uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9cb9d2c0c232b63c58dbaf314fb8f56ef63b2901","tid":2087120,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:55:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%83%E6%97%AC%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89%E6%89%8B%E6%8D%89%E8%AD%A6%E6%A3%8D-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E9%98%BB%E5%B7%AE%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC-%E7%8D%B2%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E5%80%99%E8%A8%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%2597%25AC%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25BD%2594%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%258D%2589%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25A3%258D-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%2580%2599%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=96e0c9d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%2597%25AC%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25BD%2594%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%258D%2589%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25A3%258D-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%2580%2599%25E8%25A8%258A%2F&h=1f4bb45e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%83%E6%97%AC%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89%E6%89%8B%E6%8D%89%E8%AD%A6%E6%A3%8D-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E9%98%BB%E5%B7%AE%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC-%E7%8D%B2%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E5%80%99%E8%A8%8A/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年 9 月 29 日有市民發起「全球反極權大遊行」，當日一名 71 歲清潔工人被指在銅鑼灣崇光百貨外捉住一名警員的警棍，妨礙警方工作。他被控一項阻撓在正當執行職務的警務人員罪，今（30 日）在東區裁判法院提堂。辯方申請押後案件至 8 月 11 日，待索取文件及提供法律意見，被告獲准繼續保釋。<br />\n<br />\n被告郭豪強（清潔工人，71 歲），被控於去年 9  月 29 日銅鑼灣軒尼詩道 555 號崇光百貨（銅鑼灣）外，故意阻撓在正當執行職務的警務人員，即警員 18570 。據了解，被告見當時現場有警員向不知名人士揮動警棍，期間涉嫌上前出手捉住警棍。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC1329/2020"},{"pid":"46de165db6360802128bdc67a70d178ce81f39cf","tid":2087120,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:55:36.000Z","msg":"佢絕對唔係廢老"},{"pid":"38f65090de09278cfc6e21d172ff03506989627b","tid":2087120,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://na.cx/i/x0vodRn.png&amp;h=bffec503&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z74Hva5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ74Hva5.png&h=a1d38e47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"baeb8db234d446f205b583eac7e86ddf01295724","tid":2087120,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138f8838b8b749447b21eba09de687c3979934dc","tid":2087120,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望唔洗坐"},{"pid":"0a2037d4cc60f3bbc42db7a8b612266fbeffe340","tid":2087120,"uid":2397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:57:46.000Z","msg":"勇過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以聽日要出黎"},{"pid":"a3182769c61b016e7ede697f587c3d454d38fec1","tid":2087120,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frow